Title: Vientos and Lindor Power Mets to Dominant 8-3 Win Over Royals ⚾
Description: The Mets soared to an 8-3 victory over the Royals, with Vientos driving in 3 runs and Lindor smashing his 19th homer. Juan Soto added his 22nd homer, marking back-to-back blasts for the Mets. Lindor now has 29 homers and 81 RBIs against Kansas City, his top stats against any team. Huascar Brazobán improved to 5-2 with a solid performance. Discover what’s next for these stars and how they continue to dominate!
